abstract: United Health/Oxford, the largest health insurer in New York State, agrees to drop a fight to keep its filings for rate increases secret, putting pressure on other insurance carriers to follow suit.
snippet: United Health/Oxford, the largest health insurer in New York, has reached an agreement over transparency in its filings for premium increases, putting pressure on other insurers to follow suit.
lead_paragraph: United Health/Oxford, the largest health insurer in New York, has reached an agreement over transparency in its filings for premium increases, putting pressure on other insurers to follow suit.
